  ====
  - [[Page~67 (4)霞]]
    ==
    - Clouds tinged red [[Kangxi: 赤雲氣也 etc., 通作赮]];
    - vapor, smokiness;
    - _mok(9) (4)h(a/) m(o\)(6)_
        [[mok6 haa4 mou6 莫霞霧]]
        don't move about so, be still;
    - _(4)h(a/) p(')(u/)i(3)_
        [[haa4 pui3 霞珮]]
