  ==
  - Williams' 霞珮: Whilst 珮 is literally a jade ornament,
    the rendering as "robe" is correct.
    See the Cantonese opera 《紫釵記》, which has 戴鳳冠、披霞珮
    ("put on [the] phoenix crown, [and] drape [the] sky-red ornamental [robe]").
  ==
